---
title: Premium Fillet Steak & Creamy Truffle Sauce for Dinner with Pear & Chocolate Chip Crumble for Dessert
description: Dish up tender premium beef eye fillet with a divine creamy truffle sauce, plus crispy chunks of Parmesan-roasted potato and
sautéed greens that complement all the rich flavours. Then, tuck into a luxe dessert featuring our new and totally delicious pear
and choc chip crumble. It's hard to beat simple and classic, but it's sure easy to give it a snazzy makeover.

